## React/Next.js
- Place components in `src/components/**`; use `.tsx` files.
- Add `'use client'` when using client-only APIs/hooks.
- Follow Rules of Hooks; include exhaustive-deps.
- JSX:
  - No prop spreading.
  - JSX only in `.tsx`.
  - Component names in `PascalCase`.
- Next config: `next.config.ts` uses `devIndicators: false`.
